strings: <voice_0x010009BE><se_low>King Trode: So? What happened? Did you do what the young girl asked? Hm? Well?

<voice_0x010009BF><se_low>King Trode: WHAT!? Dhoulmagus killed Master Rylus!?
The same Dhoulmagus we're looking for?
<voice_0x010009C0><se_low>King Trode: That fiend killed his own teacher!?
<voice_0x010009C1><se_low>King Trode: And you say he headed south?

<voice_0x010009C2><se_low>King Trode: Then there's no time to lose, <hero>!
We must go after him at once!
<voice_0x010009C3><se_low>King Trode: Let's be on our way!
